<plot>Using actual police footage gathered from around Britain and overseas, Alastair Stewart presents an insight into the often bizarre and terrifying behaviour of the world's motorists. For whatever reasons, be it speed, recklessness, or driver fatigue or intoxication, the world's roads are often dangerous places. Also shown are the innovative methods police are using to combat these problems.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?437729</url></doc>
